\c 29
\s Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* ngeGibhithe
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wetshumi, ng\add enyanga\add* yetshumi, ngolwetshumi lambili lwenyanga, ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kimi, lisithi:
\v 2 Ndodana yomuntu, misa ubuso bakho\x + 6.2.\x* bumelene loFaro inkosi yeGibhithe\x + Jer. 44.30.\x*, uprofethe umelene laye\x + 6.2.\x*, njalo umelene layo yonke iGibhithe\x + Isa. 19.1. Jer. 25.19.\x*.
\v 3 Khuluma uthi: Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Khangela, ngimelane lawe, Faro, nkosi yeGibhithe\x + 29.10. 30.22.\x*, umgobho omkhulu olele phakathi kwemifula yawo\x + 32.2.\x*\x + Isa. 27.1. 51.9. Jer. 46.22. Hlab. 44.19. 74.13. Isa. 30.6.\x*, othi: Umfula wami ngowami, ngazenzela \add wona\x + 29.9. 28.2.\x*\add*.
\v 4 Kodwa ngizafaka izingwegwe emihlathini yakho\x + 19.9. 38.4. 2 Kho. 19.28.\x*, ngenze inhlanzi zemifula yakho zinamathele emaxolweni akho\x + Levi 11.9.\x*, ngikukhuphule phakathi kwemifula yakho, lazo zonke inhlanzi zemifula yakho zizanamathela emaxolweni akho\x + Levi 11.9.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo ngizakutshiya enkangala, wena lazo zonke inhlanzi zemifula yakho\x + 32.4.\x*; uzawela ebusweni beganga; kawuyikuhlanganiswa, kawuyikubuthwa\x + Jer. 8.2. 25.33. Seb. 5.6. 8.2.\x*; ngizakunikela ube yikudla kuzo izilo zeganga lenyoni zamazulu\x + Jer. 34.20.\x*.
\v 6 Labo bonke abahlali beGibhithe bazakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 6.7. 29.9,16,21.\x*\nd*, ngoba bebeludondolo lomhlanga kuyo indlu kaIsrayeli\x + 2 Kho. 18.21. Isa. 36.6.\x*.
\v 7 Lapho bekubamba ngesandla, wephula wadabula lonke ihlombe labo; lalapho beseyama kuwe\x + 17.15,17. Isa. 20.5. 30.3,5. Jer. 2.36. Jer. 37.5,7,11.\x*, wephuka, wenza zonke inkalo zabo zama\x + Hlab. 69.23.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Ngakho itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Khangela, ngizaletha inkemba phezu kwakho\x + 14.17. 30.4. 32.11,12.\x*, ngiqume kusuke kuwe umuntu lenyamazana\x + 14.17. 30.4. 32.11,12.\x*.
\v 9 Lelizwe leGibhithe lizakuba yincithakalo lenkangala. Khona bezakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 29.9,16,21. 6.7.\x*\nd*. Ngoba uthe: Umfula ngowami, mina-ke ngi\add w\add*enzile\x + 29.9. 28.2.\x*.
\v 10 Ngakho, khangela, ngimelene lawe\x + 29.10. 30.22.\x*, ngimelene lemifula yakho\x + 30.12.\x*; ngenze ilizwe leGibhithe libe yizincithakalo isibili \add le\add*nkangala\x + 30.12.\x*, kusukela emphotshongweni kusiya eSevene\x + 30.6.\x* kuze kube semngceleni weEthiyophiya\x + Zef. 3.10.\x*.
\v 11 Kakulanyawo lomuntu oluzadlula kilo, kakulanyawo lwenyamazana oluzadlula kilo; futhi kaliyikuhlalwa \add okwe\add*minyaka engamatshumi amane\x + 32.13. 35.7.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba ngizakwenza ilizwe leGibhithe \add libe\add* yincithakalo phakathi kwamazwe wonke achithekileyo\x + 30.7.\x*; lemizi yalo phakathi kwemizi engamanxiwa izakuba yincithakalo \add okwe\add*minyaka engamatshumi amane\x + 30.7.\x*; njalo ngizahlakaza amaGibhithe phakathi kwezizwe, ngiwasabalalise emazweni\x + 30.23,26. Jer. 46.19.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Ngoba itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Ekupheleni kweminyaka engamatshumi amane ngizabutha amaGibhithe ebantwini abahlakazekele khona\x + Isa. 19.23. Jer. 46.26.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo ngizabuyisela abathunjwa beGibhithe\x + 16.53.\x*, ngibenze babuyele \add e\add*lizw\add eni\add* lePatrosi, elizweni lokuzalwa kwabo; lapho-ke bazakuba ngumbuso ophansi\x + 30.14. Isa. 11.11.\x*.
\v 15 Lizakuba phansi kulayo imibuso, futhi kalisayikuziphakamisa phezu kwezizwe; ngoba ngizabanciphisa ukuze bangabuyi babuse phezu kwezizwe\x + 30.13.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo kalisayikuba lithemba kuyo indlu kaIsrayeli\x + Isa. 30.2,3. 36.4,6. Lilo 4.17.\x*, eletha ukukhunjulwa kwesiphambeko, lapho bephenduka ukulandela bona\x + Nani 5.15.\x*. Kodwa bazakwazi ukuthi ngiyiNkosi uJehova\x + 29.6.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Kwasekusithi ngomnyaka wamatshumi amabili lesikhombisa, nge\add nyanga\add* yokuqala, ngolokuqala lwenyanga, ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kimi, lisithi:
\v 18 Ndodana yomuntu, uNebhukadirezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 26.7,8.\x* wenza ibutho lakhe lakhonza inkonzo enkulu\x + Jer. 25.9.\x* limelene leTire\x + Isa. 23.1.\x*; lonke ikhanda laphucwa, lalo lonke ihlombe lasutshulwa\x + Isa. 18.2,7.\x*; kanti yena kalamvuzo, lebutho lakhe, ngenxa yeTire, ngenxa yenkonzo ayikhonza emelene layo.
\v 19 Ngakho itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Khangela, ngizanikela ilizwe leGibhithe kuNebhukadirezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 30.10,12,24,25. 32.11. Jer. 46.13.\x*; njalo uzathatha ixuku layo, athumbe ukuthunjwa kwayo, aphange impango yayo; njalo kuzakuba liholo lebutho lakhe\x + 30.4.\x*.
\v 20 Ngimnike ilizwe leGibhithe \add kube\add* ngumvuzo akhonza ngawo kulo, ngoba bangisebenzela, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + Jer. 25.9.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Ngalolosuku ngizakwenza uphondo lwendlu kaIsrayeli lukhahlele\x + Hlab. 132.17. Luka 1.69.\x*, ngikunike ukukhamisa komlomo phakathi kwabo\x + 16.63. 24.27. 33.22.\x*. Njalo bazakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 29.6.\x*\nd*.
